section.section:
This subsection does not prevent a transfer that:
is part of a reorganization under § 8-301 of the State Government Article;
is needed to comply with federal law or a policy directive of a federal unit that relates to the use of federal funds;
because of an emergency declared by the Governor, is needed to protect the health, welfare, or property of the public; or
is specifically authorized by the budget bill or other law.
